name: MedsenseHealth
0:
”Alexa, open medsense health”
”When should I take my next medication?”
”Did I take my medication from the blue container?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: medsense health
Developer Terms of Use
des: Medsense Health is a voice-enabled Alexa Skill for the Medsense Health application. To get started, turn on Alexa notifications in the Medsense Health mobile application. Next, you will link your account by going into "Settings" and pressing "Link Account". After pressing "Link Account", you will log in using your Medsense Health account username and password. Next, turn on "Reminders" and "Alexa Notifications" and save your permissions. Once this is done, say "Alexa, open Medsense" and follow the voice instructions to receive your alerts and notifications!
